-- NYC Water Authority Increases Build America Sale 50% to Raise $750 Million
-- B y   A l e x a n d r a   H a r r i s
-- 2010-11-09T22:07:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/nyc-water-authority-increases-build-america-sale-50-to-raise-750-million.html
New York City Municipal Water Finance
Authority, which raises funds for the water and sewer system in
the most populous U.S. city, sold $750 million in Build America
Bonds today, a 50 percent increase from its initial offering,
according to an agency press release.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Alexandra Harris  in New York at 
 aharris48@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mark Tannenbaum at 
 mtannen@bloomberg.net . 